OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells at first, however
OL,7,Fcloud amounts should increase from the
OL,8,Feast for a time, perhaps bringing the
OL,9,Fodd spot of light rain. Becoming
OL,10,Fclearer again towards dawn, perhaps
OL,11,Fwith local rural grass frost in
OL,12,Fwestern parts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FEarly cloud soon clearing
OL,15,Fwestwards to leave a mainly fine day
OL,16,Fwith sunny spells. Temperatures near-
OL,17,Fnormal, but tempered by the
OL,18,Fstrengthening easterly wind,
OL,19,Fespecially in coastal districts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
