OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWindy
OL,6,Fmidweek, but mainly fine in this
OL,7,Fperiod. Some cloudy starts are likely,
OL,8,Fespecially in eastern areas, with
OL,9,Fwestern parts likely brightest.
